                                        <rect key="frame" x="0.0" y="161" width="355" height="0.0"/>
                                        <string key="text">During street sweeping season (April - November) the Chicago Department of Streets and Sanitation uses mechanical street sweepers to remove debris and litter from streets, weather permitting.</string>
